reviewText: All the good ones. And all in one package.
This was when they made movies ! At least that 's what my daughter says !
Oh, what a nice quad of movies... comes with four separate DVDs and my favorite of the 4 is Jagged Edge,of which was so good, I don't even remember the other 3. The edge is great.
Like the combination of movies included in this pack.  It has my 2 favs as well as 2 others that were big in the day.  Great Price too!
All my favorite movies from the 80's at such a good price!! Loved It! My favorite is About Last night.
Great compilation! I loved the appearance of Kid Creole and the Coconuts performing "My Male Curiosity" in Against All Odds.
All good movies that I do not mind watching once in a while without having to rent them over and over.
I am pleased with the product.
